  "texts": [
    "Queueing and Batching Policies We compare simple FIFO dispatch with a length-aware batching (LAB) policy.",
    "LAB takes the head-of-line request and batches it with other requests whose lengths closely match the head-of-line request.",
    "It is widely adopted (e.g., ORCA (Yu et al., 2022), Sarathi (Agrawal et al., 2023)) and serves as the strongest length-aware baseline.",
    "Figure 9 illustrates the latency benefit of this strategy.",
    "LAB consistently achieves lower TPOT compared to FIFO (reducing latency by 1-2 ms) across all workloads."
  ],
